From c6538a4787cb165d7158033415c3dffd62bc5cbe Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ksenia Lepikhina <klepikhina@ghx.com>
Date: Thu, 9 Apr 2026 15:04:38 -0600
Subject: [PATCH] Redesign website with nature-inspired theme and storytelling
 focus

- Add nature color palette (forest greens, sky blues, earth tones)
- Create card-based layouts for adventure listings
- Add dropdown navigation for Adventures and Regions
- Build interactive D3 adventure map on homepage
- Convert books page to radial tree visualization with stats
- Add adventure statistics with donut/bar charts
- Create region pages for filtering by location
- Add writing section and update creative hub
- Migrate 22 posts with enhanced front matter (coordinates, featured images)
